run() - Method in class main.Customer
For each customer, a thread on this Customer object eats the three courses in the correct orderby calling the eat() method in the corresponding Table, prints out what course this Customer is eating, and sleeps for a random time between 0 & 4 seconds to mimic time taken to eat.
run() - Method in class main.Waiter
For each customer, a thread on this Waiter object serves the three courses in the correct orderby calling the serve() method in the corresponding Table, prints out what course is served to which Customer, and sleeps for a random time between 0 & 4 seconds to mimic time taken in serving.
